'''Taɣit tameqqṛant''' neɣ '''Asakka ameqṛan''' (S [[Taspenyult|Tespenyult]]: ''Gran cañón'', S [[Taglizit|Teglizit]]: ''Grand canyon'', S [[tutlayt n Hopi]]: ''Ongtupqa'', S [[tutlayt n Yavapai]]: ''Wi:kaʼi:la'') d [[taɣit (tarakalt)|asakka]] alqayan hraw s waṭas, yezga-d deg wamur agafan utrim n uwanak n [[Arizona]] deg [[Iwunak Yeddukklen n Temrikt|Yiwunak Yeddukklen]], Yessentay (ibeddu-d) seg [[Idurar n Ṛuky|yidurar n Ṛuky]] alamma d tiftisin n [[California]] s teɣzi n 349 km ma d tilqi-ynes tafellayt tettawaṭ ar 1740 m, Taɣit tameqrant temmug-d s usrag (ssebba) n waman n [[Asif n Colorado|wasif n Colorado]] i yezgan teččen w ssefsayen iẓṛa n [[Agni n Colorado|wegni n Colorado]] di teɣzi n 40 n imelyan n iseggasen ayen i d-yeglan s teflalit n [[tissi|tissiwin]] n tegnit yemgaraden i d-innulfan deg 2 n imelyaṛen n iseggasen yezrin deg umezruy [[tasnakalt|asnaklan]] n [[amenẓaw|umenẓaw]] n [[Tamrikt n Ugafa|Marikan tagafant]] 

 
